                        through federal programs. Review the refusal reasons, address any issues, and
                        consider other pathways. Some provinces allow appeals or reconsideration requests.
                    </div>
                </details>

                <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg mb-3 not-prose">
                    <summary class="p-4 font-bold cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50">
                        Is PNP easier than Express Entry?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="p-4 pt-0 text-slate-600">
                        It depends on your profile. PNP can be easier if you have a job offer or connections
                        to a specific province but lack the high CRS score needed for Express Entry draws.
                        However, PNP streams are competitive too, with limited nominations available each year.
